omberg.com/s/c/D8gMAjR_F4MLVTaxjXwcjEmEvm2QnDIZEKsuAkbHTpqjLOOmOVnVvqJ8FjwPbYl4PoUvnKbH4wh4djnidCGIrtH54xv4pMmZK8_Ebf0iP5HXsXGsz1tGAWxF75dI4mIMV43ff2wn2RrKDM3mRyuUhU7PiZUED9nSkHa8y8xkoMFLbDdGTu1Jpgr6n7un_fY6QdLRqu6iAHzw4wXpKNeS9mGiGUAfk_l4hXksupM4qeLuq7ws4Hj3BZK4B4X27uxdtOakSf_lKRgwt2F78Hcm6hu0kMOMJSCpuheqyA0NgztL9wXqv4K7gtA1IasXga1KrZtwkLglDqAS9iRvmX47hyTnGgsf38bZplWrluUSRPQgssLlBK3bS1QxHD8Ska0wLi0qXvANz_WaFOztdVJwMeJmcuS7qHGxbwY1ga5KIMDqirco_P0Voxb27fw0K1LpZQBaW8EtD46t6gEOUL5_EH7MAVzMIacFD7vf6U2RI-ekFW4qJ_pooEFCfyah0Q/EwWQdlnFcNhVrz6vlKmSlxsWOw3Ckakj/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普支持帕克斯顿而非科宁竞选德克萨斯州参议员"&gt;极右翼盟友&lt;/a&gt;得克萨斯州总检察长肯·帕克斯顿，与现任共和党参议员约翰·科宁的决选日益个人化且成本高昂。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/8dUzSpQ_oC-gJhjW6ddmxg1ibjI9EqW-E-HsslNp1oFFoDb-VfTzVR5rb7ww0GH25vyfcWDmLH3GT-efvWXb8NhSuTq8x8PUiKa2vNLHa1cKvpqW8XNKXvbvoo8D3y5WEFtublNt87AW0Jibm0TyDl1csDXEDvIKc0OUKwyACQUJskz0C0U_DE2C-yluSCY6RBZj46Rjqaicdu1aLmXOixWD165YG_OuEophXiaZThy5uehqCdf3B5mBLc_ApfvCLqMqNkzpiQPRnWEVHeK4B1l682tCKpyF3T0a4ZcE3e7xtkwCJ9XYoalr0VPGcUvDK18rP6uxuaENwvwehzp75F3P2v5WUBTv9a6iEdKN2LkOEXUnLPFnOfn79rfDBp7I0fhO1hC4CKxz9TOwHuuWEyrn4Ed2bAAYb8bBHxVSmKd3wEJc7xJyFpnVDjRMsutid03vWnXMBOuOSglu65pb93wJG-YiIwkfzWUYevqTCQWUgpd5AJrgHDVr8pP9gpQMR8YguIo/QwaqPnmBxH12vdAbsYR2ACerL-2xCPGc/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="特朗普在德克萨斯州参议员竞选中选择帕克斯顿而非现任科宁"&gt;此举的时机令人震惊&lt;/a&gt;。这也可能激怒得克萨斯州和国会山的许多共和党领导人，他们曾支持科宁，这位四届参议员曾被视为潜在的多数党领袖。去年大部分时间里，科宁在民意调查中落后于帕克斯顿，但在 3 月 3 日的初选投票中，科宁重新领先，获得了约 42% 的支持率，而帕克斯顿则获得了近 41% 的支持率。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/eAkhxylVAxRQTlBYxNICWbEketVNtnIZlJDrTK0hgY-ZGD7lR0wcPv8IghweDYk0julaW0KB3CDyA4hdex-N0hJ6fU4p5p4pz06WiHphy2httSpijLfEQ8MNeW-4DG89H6tX_CRaIQs2YPoaDur1DpB083biKiwlgLVvndz9jW8X7UKH2dTx_q6_pewd-7vJacqLxNDeNjaV4Rzk